🌍 AI Translator Agent (Gemini + Chainlit)

An intelligent AI Translator Agent built with Google Gemini, Python, and Chainlit.
It can translate between Urdu and English based on the user’s needs — just like chatting with a multilingual assistant!

🚀 Features

🔤 Translates between English ↔ Urdu

🧠 Uses Google Gemini 2.0 Flash for accurate and context-aware translations

💬 Built with Chainlit for a clean, interactive chat UI

⚙️ Maintains conversation history for smooth interactions

🔒 Keeps API keys secure using .env

🧩 Tech Stack

Python 3.10+

Gemini API (Google Generative Language)

Agents Framework

Chainlit

dotenv

Install dependencies

pip install -r requirements.txt


Set up your environment variables
Create a .env file and add:

GEMINI_API_KEY=your_api_key_here


Run the app

chainlit run main.py

💡 How It Works

The app initializes a Gemini-powered agent that understands user queries.

It detects the desired translation direction (Urdu ↔ English).

Messages are managed through Chainlit’s session system for a chat-like experience.

Responses are generated dynamically using Gemini’s reasoning capabilities.

🔮 Future Enhancements

🌐 Multi-language support (French, Arabic, Spanish, etc.)

🗣️ Voice input & speech translation

💾 Translation history and export options

